  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Syrio_Forel\" title=\"Syrio Forel\">Syrio</a> says that every hurt is a lesson, and every lesson makes you stronger.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Eddard VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404023251\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 82/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 309/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.924      1 -total\n100.00%    3.924      1 Template:Ref\n 62.13%    2.438      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26759-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404023251 and revision id 245347\n -->\n",
